title: Sage Kotsenburg "I Ride Neffland"
description: Watch as Neff snowboarder and 2014 Winter Olympian, Sage Kotsenburg, tears up Neffland. Kotsenburg has a blast while casually shredding the candy cane rails and cupcake boxes of Neffland. Neffland is located within the Park City Mountain Resort in Park City, Utah. The video also features special guest Max Warbington. Enjoy while the two rip it up together. Filmed and edited by Pat Fenelon.
